  "title": "Sales Assistant [Home/Kitchen Product | Part-time] (ML06)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Sales Assistant (Part-time)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Location: Millenia Walk / VivoCity</p>\n<p>Working days: Friday + Weekend</p>\n<p>Working Hours: 12 pm-8 pm (Friday) &amp; 12pm-9pm (Weekend)</p>\n<p>Salary: $13.50 per hour (Additional commission incentives offered)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>Assist with daily store operations</p>\n<p>Actively promote and demonstrate electronic and home appliance products to customers</p>\n<p>Provide accurate product information and recommendations</p>\n<p>Help achieve sales targets through proactive customer engagement</p>\n<p>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the store</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>Previous experience in promoting home or kitchen products is required</p>\n<p>Available to work on Fridays and weekends.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📩 Welcome to apply through WhatsApp, Please send me your resume.</p>\n<p>📱WhatsApp: ‪‪‪‪‪‪+65 8928 7217‬‬‬‬‬ (‬Contact person: Mandy Lu）</p>\n<p>🔗 ‪‪‪‪‪https://wa.me/6589287217‬‬</p>\n<p><br></p>",
